    public class MinimalGeneEnricher
extends AbstractInteractorEnricher<Gene>
    A basic minimal enricher for genes. See description of minimal enrichment in AbstractInteractorEnricher. The GeneFetcher is required for enriching genes.
    Since:
    04/09/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
